.  E                   Am
   Buyugimsan doimo Iso

[V2]
.   Am        G         Am
 // Minnatdormiz Sendan Xudovand
.F        G               Am
 Bizni sevib qutqarganing-chun
.Am                  G    Am
 Sen bilan yashaylik doimo
.F         G           Am
 Qutqaruvchim Iso Masihim //</lyrics>
